{"tid":1960282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳： 收工男一拖三 港台hea嗌 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-04-06T05:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T05:48:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"29d782bd273ee4de599ffdcc5838ec8e862dc179","tid":1960282,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200406/F4ISZ6WWIIZUO25DCDRV57MD6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200406%2FF4ISZ6WWIIZUO25DCDRV57MD6E%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLcTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=90083861\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200406%2FF4ISZ6WWIIZUO25DCDRV57MD6E%2F&h=9d62db9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200406/F4ISZ6WWIIZUO25DCDRV57MD6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n收工男一拖三 港台hea嗌 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200406/large/1586104511_2e85.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586104511_2e85.gif&h=18a70ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n傅振中噚日帶三人去港台示威，相比之下，左方嘅記者陣容鼎盛得多。何家達攝<br />\n<br />\n最近左派全力狙擊港台，一班成日示威博上左報交數嘅常客又輪流現身，今次輪到保衞香港運動嘅傅振中，佢噚日帶住三人去港台門口示威，要求港台炒喺港台節目《The Pulse》問世衞會否重新考慮台灣會員資格嘅記者唐若韞。<br />\n<br />\n其實佢哋啲示威一向得十個八個人，但少到得四人就真係示弱咗啲，傅振中話因為「禁聚令」，所以先得四個人，但成個過程約10分鐘就散場，即使只係交數都應該專業啲，做臨記做到咁hea係冇飯盒㗎！"},{"pid":"6b3c9f00a1439f9a2b2e57f0ed0f7a226de1b065","tid":1960282,"uid":156511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"跟住黑警又可以拉撚晒d記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}